      <lg xml:id="TVM1.2.6">
<l>paṟṟila ṉīcaṉu muṟṟavu niṉṟaṉaṉ</l>
<l>paṟṟilai yāyavaṉ muṟṟi laṭaṅkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is without attachment and the lord totally stands [there].</l>
<l>You being without attachment yield to his perfection.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
